##Flight of Glory

A 3D dogfight versus game. Written in C# (XNA) for Xbox360. 

Features:
- 2 players
- Different aircrafts to choose from
- Radar system
- Large city map
- Obstacles to be avoided while chasing your opponent

How to run the project:
1) Download the source code
2) Launch the .sln file
3) Press F5 and you are ready

NOTE:
Requires 2 Xbox360 controllers to play.

